Package: lossratio
Type: Package
Title: Loss Ratio Analysis for Insurance Experience Data
Version: 0.0.0.9000
Authors@R:
    person(given = "Seokhoon", family = "Joo", email = "seokhoonj@gmail.com",
           role = c("aut", "cre"))
Description: A toolkit for analysing insurance loss ratios using structured
    experience data with loss and risk premium. Loss ratio is defined as
    loss divided by risk premium. Provides underwriting-period,
    calendar-period, and total aggregation frameworks with cumulative
    metrics, margin analysis, and composition diagnostics. Intended for
    actuarial workflows and extended with reserving methods such as
    chain ladder.
